abstract: The figures set the stage for the car industry to end the year on a high note.
snippet: The figures set the stage for the car industry to end the year on a high note.
lead_paragraph: DETROIT  New-vehicle sales in the United States rose nearly 17 percent in November, setting the stage for the industry to end the year on a high note and enter 2011 with considerable momentum.

headline.main: Car Sales Post Strong Gains, With Toyota as the Exception
headline.print_headline: Car Sales Post Strong Gains, With Toyota as the Exception
